# 🎨 Crazy Favicon Generator

A **free, non-commercial favicon generator** for creating custom website icons with ease. Generate favicons in multiple sizes from text, upload custom fonts, and download complete icon packages.

![Favicon Generator](https://img.shields.io/badge/Tool-Favicon%20Generator-blue?style=flat-square)
![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-Free%20Educational-green?style=flat-square)
![GDPR](https://img.shields.io/badge/Privacy-GDPR%20Compliant-purple?style=flat-square)
![GitHub](https://img.shields.io/badge/Purpose-Educational-brightgreen?style=flat-square)
![GitHub](https://img.shields.io/badge/Status-Demo-orange?style=flat-square)
![Trademark](https://img.shields.io/badge/Logo-Trademarked-red?style=flat-square)

## ✨ Features

- 🎯 **Text to Favicon** - Generate icons from letters with custom fonts
- 🖼️ **Image Upload** - Convert your own images to favicons
- 🎨 **Multiple Effects** - Stroke, glow, gradient, emboss effects
- 📐 **Various Shapes** - Circle, square, triangle, rounded, sketchy
- 🎛️ **Position Controls** - Fine-tune text and background positioning
- 📦 **Complete Package** - Generate all standard favicon sizes
- 🔤 **Custom Fonts** - Upload and use your own fonts
- 🌈 **Background Effects** - Gradients, shadows, strokes, and more
- 📱 **PWA Ready** - Includes manifest.json generation

## 📚 Educational Repository Notice

This GitHub repository is provided for **educational and demonstration purposes only**:

- 🎓 **Learning Resource** - Study modern web development techniques
- 🔍 **Code Reference** - Examine frontend JavaScript and canvas manipulation
- 🚫 **Not for Commercial Use** - See licensing section below
- ™️ **Trademark Protected** - Logo and branding elements reserved

**Perfect for learning:** Canvas API, File handling, Font processing, CSS effects, PWA implementation

## 🚀 Quick Start

1. **Visit the Tool** - Open `index.html` in your browser
2. **Enter Text** - Type your favicon text (e.g., "CFG")
3. **Choose Style** - Select colors, effects, and shapes
4. **Customize** - Fine-tune positioning and fonts
5. **Download** - Get individual PNG files or complete package

## 🎯 Use Cases

- **Personal Projects** - Create unique favicons for hobby websites
- **Learning Web Development** - Understand favicon implementation
- **Prototyping** - Quick favicon generation for mockups
- **Open Source Projects** - Free alternative to paid tools

## 🔧 Technical Details

### Generated Files
- `favicon-16x16.png` - Browser tabs
- `favicon-32x32.png` - Bookmark bars
- `favicon-180x180.png` - iOS Safari
- `favicon-192x192.png` - Android Chrome
- `favicon-512x512.png` - High resolution displays
- `manifest.json` - PWA configuration
- Complete HTML snippet for easy integration

### Browser Support
- ✅ Chrome (all versions)
- ✅ Firefox (all versions)  
- ✅ Safari (all versions)
- ✅ Edge (all versions)
- ✅ Mobile browsers

## 📋 Font Licensing

### Default Font
